import React from 'react'
import { Form } from 'semantic-ui-react'

export default function PointSpender(props) {
    return (
        <Form inverted>
            <Form.Field label={props.name + " Score:"} control='select'>
            <option value={[0, 8]}>8 (0 points)</option>
            <option value={[0, 8]}>9 (1 point)</option>
            <option value={[0, 8]}>10 (2 points)</option>
            <option value={[0, 8]}>11 (3 points)</option>
            <option value={[0, 8]}>12 (4 points)</option>
            <option value={[0, 8]}>13 (5 points)</option>
            <option value={[0, 8]}>14 (7 points)</option>
            <option value={[0, 8]}>15 (9 points)</option>
            </Form.Field>
        </Form>
    )
}
